a.xlink:title: Adds an ExactCard to the specified zone.
Helper function to add a card to a specific deck zone.
Adds a card using the preferred printing if available.
Adds a printing of the card to the specified zone (Mainboard or Sideboard).
Adds a card to the main deck or sideboard based on Ctrl key.
Adds a card to the sideboard explicitly.
Swaps a card in the deck view.
Adds a printing to the mainboard zone.
Adds a printing to the sideboard zone.
Offsets the card count at the specified index by the given amount.
